==German==
===Etymology===
Old High German ''[[untar]]'', akin to Old Saxon ''undar''
===Preposition===
'''unter'''

#[[under]]
#[[below]]
#[[among]]

''Note:'' The preposition "unter" is used with accusative case if the verb shows movement from one place to another, whereas it is used with dative case if the verb shows location.

